\id COL KƆL - Bible Iyansi 
\h KƆLƆSAY 
\toc1 Un'kaan akà Akɔlɔsay 
\toc2 KƆLƆSAY 
\toc3 Kɔl 
\mt2 Un'kaan akà 
\mt1 Akɔlɔsay 
\imt1 Nsɛmà 
\ip Kɔlɔsay làkäl bul mwɛy là Azi Minɔ̈ɔ̈r, ŋàbà bàfàbel naa Türki, tsütsü a Ɛfɛsɔ kà isii a kilɔmɛtrɛ nkam yweel. Ikaswaŋà naa Pɔl bul alà kàtöl anki akà ikikye. Ɛpafras, un'nsi Kɔlɔsay nde ŋakwo, umwɛy uboo a asyääl ande, kàkäl mbuur atàtwɛb musyen Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ kwo. 
\ip Abun, Pɔl kàkäl mbuur a bɔlokà mbalà yumwɛy u Lɔmà. Ɛpafras kàyi mukun'kyään naa baar a Kɔlɔsay bàbilà uboo a an'lɔɔŋ a akyään a an'lɔɔŋ akün. Akyään abà bàyilɔŋà naa muyöb Nzam anà muwà mɔ̈ɔ̈, bàtàkömà bàngwal a an'dweelà, ukyey nkyɛɛy anà nswɛɛŋ a ngwalàngwal, unsà ndaa iler isa adyà, man ... Pa bun'kyään ndaa a mpay ayi, ntööm kàsöön baar a Kɔlɔsay mukayɔɔb naa mɔ̈ɔ̈ ufàpà Nzam amu Yɛsu Klistɔ wàŋàkwo mbɔɔn a mbɔɔn. Nde waa katööm mbalà yumwɛy a Tishik anà Ɔnɛsim. Un'kaan awà wàŋàkab itiir itär: 
\ip Itiir atàtwɛb kyàmuswaŋ ikɔ̈b a Klistɔ: nde wà udu a ngwal a an'dweelà yanswà, anà nde mpɛl awà Mfum a Ikööŋ. 
\ip Itiir kyàyweel: ntööm wàmusà baar a Kɔlɔsay unsà igyɛɛŋ ntɔn ibii a baar asin bàmuyipay akà ba. 
\ip Itiir kyà ntsüü kyàmuswaŋ nkääl a mɔ̈ɔ̈ akün yan'kwo mukal unsà un'tüüb anà Klistɔ, uboo a ikööŋ a Klistɔ kyaŋakwo, uboo a bɔr itàkal uboo a baar banswà. 
\ip Ntsülà yàmuswaŋ akyeey a mbɔɔn a mbɔɔn anà mbɔr aŋàsɔn u kɔɔ a ntööm ŋakwo. 
\ip An'lɔɔŋ an'be man'kwo màsɔɔm ifà anà isin a paŋà làmwɛy anà lumwɛy. Wɛɛ ma mun'tüüb mwɛy: ma màfàpà aklistɔ mpiim unsà làkwikilà aba amu Klistɔ mwɛy. Kyakin, ntääŋ a un'kaan akà baar a Kɔlɔsay yà ndaa mwɛy yipepey: ya ifàtɛn ngwalngwal ikɔ̈b a ngyee a Klistɔ, nde mbuur afàbeen asɔ a an'dweelà. 
\ie  
\c 1  
\s1 Mbɔr 
\p  
\v 1 Pɔl, ntööm a Yɛsu Klistɔ, unsà ukwen a Nzam, anà un'tɔŋ Tumàtɛ awà tsütsü apà mɛ, mɛ an'pà mbɔr  
\v 2 akà aŋin'kyɛɛl abà u bul a Kɔlɔsay abà atɔŋ abi unsà un'tüüb aba amu Klistɔ: wɛy kab a ngway anà duu a Nzam, Taaràbi, màkäl anà bɛ! 
\s1 Ngyamàkà a an'tɔɔn 
\p  
\v 3 Bi ifuur an'tɔɔn akà Nzam, Taar a Mwol abi Yɛsu Klistɔ, unsà ngyamàkà mpa ifàyɔn bi mupà akà nde ntɔn bɛ.  
\v 4 Bi kàwem làkwikilà abɛ amu Yɛsu Klistɔ anà ukwen làbà bɛ abà ntɔn aŋin'kyɛɛl banswà.  
\v 5 Bya byan'fà unsà làkyän alà u du ntɔn bɛ, làkyän làyöb bɛ u mbwo a ndaa a ndandaa ayà Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ alà làkɔlà akà bɛ.  
\v 6 La làpää u mɛɛn manswà, waa làbör imbɛŋ, ifà imwɛy sye ufàkyer nde amu bɛ fà ilä làwɛl bɛ anà làyöb bɛ kab a Nzam unsà ndandaa ande,  
\v 7 asànaa naa kàlalɔŋ Ɛpafras. Nde wà un'baay a isal ifàkwen bi, un'syääl a lää wà Klistɔ.  
\v 8 Nde mbuur kikyään naa ukwen nà Dweelà we abà uboo a bɛ. 
\p  
\v 9 Kyakin, akà bi, fà ilä kàwem bi abà, bi kàyɔ̈n anki muyamà ntɔn bɛ. Bi kan'lɔm akà Nzam mukàlapà, u mbwo a Dweelà ande, an'yeerà anà un'yɛnà ntɔn muyöb ukwen ande.  
\v 10 Abun, bɛ làsàkal anà nkääl aŋàkwo akà Mwol ntɔn mukun'pà un'sak taaŋ lanswà. Amu ya, bɛ làsàkyer ndaa aŋàbwaŋ, làsàbɔr mbɛŋ ifà ifà anà làsàkal u ngyööb a Nzam yà ndandaa.  
\v 11 Ngwal a làkoo ande isàlabuul bàngwal amu ya yanswà, ntɔn bɛ làkwe mukaŋ mpem u ndaa yanswà anà làsi muküünà tii u ntsüü unsà un'sak.  
\v 12 Làfuur an'tɔɔn akà Taa awà kàlasi bàŋàkwo muwal kab uboo a kwal a aŋin'kyɛɛl u pɛɛlà.  
\v 13 Nde kitsü mɔ̈ɔ̈ unsà ikɔ̈b a mpib anà nde kibiil uboo a imwol a Mwan ande wànkween.  
\v 14 Amu nde bi ibà aŋàbeen, man'be abi màŋàdwääl. 
\s1 Imbuur anà isal a Klistɔ 
\p  
\v 15 Mwan awà wà idiim a Nzam mpa bàfàman u mii. Nde wà Mwan atàtwɛb u nkyeer yanswà,  
\v 16 ntɔn indiir byanswà bàkyer amu nde, u du anà u mɛɛn, abyà ifàmɛnà anà mpa byàfàmɛnà, An'kir Imwol, Amfum, Aŋikɔ̈b anà Aŋangwal, indiir byanswà bàkyer amu nde anà ntɔn nde,  
\v 17 anà nde wà kusà a indiir byanswà, amu nde indiir byanswà byà kà ikal abya.  
\v 18 Nde wà un'tswe a ndür ayà Ikööŋ, un'bään wàtàtwɛb uboo a akü, ntɔn muwal ikal atàtwɛb, amu indiir byanswà.  
\v 19 Ntɔn Nzam kàkwen naa inzaam ande kyanswà iyööl Mwan ande,  
\v 20 anà u mbwo a nde, nde ufuur un'tüüb ande anà indiir byanswà, u mɛɛn anà u du, musà duu u mbwo a an'kil a kulunsi ande amu nde anà ntɔn nde. 
\p  
\v 21 Kyekà, itaan bɛ làkäl angyey anà ayiiŋ a Nzam unsà an'kyän anà unsa isal abɛ byà ube.  
\v 22 Wɛɛ apanà, Nzam kan'fuur un'tüüb ande anà bɛ u mbwo a ndür a imbuur a Mwan ande yàkü ntɔn mukàlamɛɛy bàŋin'kyɛɛl kusà ande, ukɔɔn too anà an'pɛl.  
\v 23 Wɛɛ ilɔɔmà naa, u mbwo a làkwikilà, bɛ làkäl bàngwal anà bàŋàtsim, ukɔɔn akal bàŋàkaabà anà làkyän a Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ alà làwem bɛ, alà bàkyään akà ikyeer kyanswà u mɛɛn, anà amu la, mɛ, Pɔl, akyàbulà un'syääl. 
\s1 Isal a Pɔl ntɔn Ikööŋ 
\p  
\v 24 Mpalàbà, mɛ an'man un'sak unsà mpay an'fuur mɛ ayà ntɔn bɛ, ntɔn mɛ in'wàmukölà u ndür amɛ nkɔ̈ɔ̈n ayà u mpay aŋàsöön a Klistɔ, ntɔn ndür ande ayà Ikööŋ,  
\v 25 ntɔn kya, mɛ akyàbulà un'syääl u mbwo a buur kan'pɛ Nzam ntɔn bɛ: mukyään ubwaŋàbwaŋ ndaa a Nzam,  
\v 26 ndaa yàkäl ngyee fà itaan anà kàmɛɛy nde mpalàbà akà aŋin'kyɛɛl ande.  
\v 27 Nde kàkwen mukaswaŋ naa un'naaŋ a làkoo nà awà uboo a ngyee ayi ntɔn baar mpa abà Ayudà: Klistɔ amu bɛ, iswaŋà naa bɛ làbye anà làkyän muwal kab unsà làkoo a Nzam.  
\v 28 Nde awà bi ifàkyään, ifàweey anà ifàlɔŋ mbuur wanswà unsà an'yeerà manswà, ntɔn mubuul mbuur wanswà ukäl aŋàyɛl amu Klistɔ.  
\v 29 Kyakin in'fàsal mɛ anà in'fànwaan mɛ anà un'swey a ngwal ande awà afàsal a unkaak a ngwal amu mɛ. 
\c 2  
\p  
\v 1 Abun, mɛ in'kwen bɛ làyöb naa bwoor a ità nà mɛ in'fànwaan ntɔn bɛ, ntɔn baar a Lawɔdisɛ, anà ntɔn baar banswà mpa abàŋàtaman akà ikikye,  
\v 2 abà, mɛ in'kwen naa mpem aba ikäl yà un'kanà, anà ba bàkäl bàŋàtüüb unsà ukwen, bàbilà uboo a un'naaŋ ande wanswà, bàyöl a un'yɛnà ntɔn bàyöb ngyee a Nzam, ikaswaŋà naa Klistɔ.  
\v 3 Un'naaŋ a an'yeerà anà ngyööb byàŋàyee amu nde.  
\v 4 An'tɛn mɛ abà ntɔn mbuur ukɔ̈ɔ̈n akàlakur a ntweey a ntsà yà loor.  
\v 5 Ntɔn itàkal naa unsà imbuur mɛ tsütsü watɛy anà bɛ, wɛɛ unsà dweelà, mɛ in'wà anà bɛ, mɛ in'wà unsà un'sak muman naa bɛ làbàŋàtsim unsà làkwikilà amu Klistɔ. 
\s1 Klistɔ mpɛl afàpà mɔ̈ɔ̈ 
\p  
\v 6 Abun, asànaa làkyey bɛ Klistɔ Yɛsu asànaa Mwol, làkäl un'tüüb anà nde.  
\v 7 Abà, làkäl aŋàsà in'swɛy anà aŋàtɔŋ amu nde, làkäl aŋàtsim unsà làkwikilà asànaa bàlalɔŋ la, anà làkäl bàŋàsöön unsà ngyamàkà a an'tɔɔn. 
\p  
\v 8 Làkäl kà igyɛɛŋ, ntɔn mbuur ukɔ̈ɔ̈n akàlalɛɛ mbwaar a ntweey a ntsà, wɛɛ ya kàyà ndandaa anki, anà an'yeerà a loor màfàfà unsà imbuur, anà unsà ngwal ifàyaal mɛɛn, wɛɛ kà akà Klistɔ anki.  
\v 9 Ntɔn ngyööl a Nzam yanswà yà u ndür ande,  
\v 10 anà bɛ, bɛ làbà aŋàyɔl amu mbuur awà un'tswe a Imfum kyanswà anà Ikɔ̈b kyanswà. 
\p  
\v 11 Amu nde sye waa bàlakyɛy, kà nkyɛɛy ayà ufàkyer kɔɔ a mbuur anki, wɛɛ nkyɛɛy a Klistɔ ayà ifàtsuuŋ imbuur abi kyà man'be.  
\v 12 Bɛ bàladye anà nde u ndüümà, bàlawiiy sye anà nde, u mbwo a làkwikilà amu unkaak a ngwal a Nzam awà kun'wiiy uboo a akü.  
\v 13 Bɛ, bɛ baar abà làkäl aŋàkwà ntɔn mbii abɛ anà ukɔɔn nkyɛɛy a ndür abɛ, Nzam kàlapɛ mɔ̈ɔ̈ anà nde. Nde kidwääl nkul a mbii abi yanswà.  
\v 14 Nde kàdwä un'kɔɔn a ikwàndwà abi anà nswɛɛŋ awa, nde kàpiy wa, waa kàbɛɛrà wa u kulunsi.  
\v 15 Abun, Amfum anà Aŋikɔ̈b, nde kasi ipɔl ipɔl, kamɛɛy ibaŋ u mii a baar banswà, kasi unsà un'lwaaŋ a iböŋ a kulunsi. 
\p  
\v 16 Abun, wɛy naa akà mbuur mwɛy ukɔ̈ɔ̈n akàlatsüül mbar ntɔn isaa anà man, itàkal ntɔn un'kyɔm, ntɔn mukyɛɛl nsöŋ akün, itàkal saba:  
\v 17 Abin byanswà byà munii a indiir byàlàyà, wɛɛ ndandaa abya yà amu Klistɔ.  
\v 18 Twon lan'pà mbwo naa bàlatsüül mbar akà baar bàfàmɛnà naa ba bà baar a làbɔ̈ɔ̈n anà bàfàsà ngyamàkà akà akyeey. Ba bàŋàbilà afwee unsà imɛɛy aba ŋakwo. Ntɔn an'kyän a imbuur aba, ba bàŋàyam a uyɔl bàkɔ̈ɔ̈n ndöŋ.  
\v 19 Ba kà bàŋàbääb anki akà Klistɔ awà un'tswe. Kyeka, u mbwo a un'tswe waa ndür yanswà ifàwal isaa anà yàŋàtüüb a deŋ deŋ a an'kör anà nkɔn, anà in'tay unsà ngyɛɛl aya ufun'pà Nzam. 
\s1 Ukwà anà ukal anà Klistɔ 
\p  
\v 20 Kya isàkal naa bɛ làkü anà Klistɔ, anà làkyàtsuŋà unsà indiir byàfàyaal mɛɛn mà, ntɔn nkye lan'fàkyey bɛ nswɛɛŋ asànaa bɛ làfàkal kà an'kɔɔ a mɛɛn:  
\v 21 « Twon an'dyà undiir wà », « Twon an'kyee undiir wunà », « Twon an'ba wa ».  
\v 22 Nswɛɛŋ ayi yà ntɔn indiir abyà ifàtay ungö musyääl bya. Ya yà nswɛɛŋ anà an'lɔɔŋ a imbuur.  
\v 23 Inye, nswɛɛŋ ayi ifàmɛnà asànaa ya ye anà an'yeerà, ntɔn ya ifàlɔm naa mbuur mbuur usi ngyamàkà asànaa ukwen mpem ande, anà làbɔ̈ɔ̈n a loor, anà upɛ ndür ande ŋakwo mpay. Wɛɛ ya ndöŋ yatɛy, ntɔn ya ifàpà ilään a ndür mpɛl. 
\c 3  
\p  
\v 1 Abun, isàkal naa bɛ làkyàwiyà anà Klistɔ, làleŋ indiir a du, ikal awà Klistɔ, awà wàŋàbwaay u kɔɔ a ibaal a Nzam.  
\v 2 Làpɛ an'kyän abɛ unsà indiir a du, wɛɛ kà unsà byàmɛɛn anki.  
\v 3 Ntɔn, bɛ làkyàkwà, mɔ̈ɔ̈ abɛ wàŋàyee uboo a Klistɔ, amu Nzam.  
\v 4 Mpal usàmɛnà Klistɔ awà mɔ̈ɔ̈ abɛ, apan, bɛ sye làsàmɛnà anà nde, unsà làkoo ande. 
\s1 Mɔ̈ɔ̈ itaan anà wàkün 
\p  
\v 5 Làdwä indiir a mɛɛn byanswà u mɔ̈ɔ̈ abɛ: ipasàsɛ, ŋingyäy, ilään, làmfɛɛl, anà unkaam abà itɛk.  
\v 6 Indiir a tub abi ifàgyool nkyɛl a Nzam udu a baan un'tswe ngwal.  
\v 7 Le nkääl làkäl bɛ anà ya, mpal làkäl bɛ uboo a mɔ̈ɔ̈ awun. 
\p  
\v 8 Wɛɛ mpalàbà, bɛ sye, làkɔɔb indiir abi byanswà: nkyɛl, itsumbuun, ful, ntwee anà ndaa a kɔɔrà abyà byàfàtoo u mun abɛ.  
\v 9 Twon lan'kur bɛ a bɛ, ntɔn bɛ làkyàkɔɔb imbuur abɛ kyà itaan anà nsyääl akya,  
\v 10 anà bɛ làkyàbwaar mbuur akün awà afàbwool taaŋ lanswà uboo a ngyööb asaŋaa isii a Nkyer ande.  
\v 11 Abun, mbuur mpa awà Un'yudà itàkal naa Un'yudà ufàkal anki, itàkal bàŋàkyɛy anà bàkɔ̈ɔ̈n aŋàkyɛy, itàkal mbuur a mbuur anà kimbuur, itàkal un'sɔ anà mbuur a nsaay, wɛɛ Klistɔ: nde wà ya yanswà amu baar banswà. 
\p  
\v 12 Ntɔn bɛ làbà aŋàsɔɔl, bà in'kyɛɛl, bànkwen akà Nzam, abun làkäl anà mpem aŋàbwaŋ, mpem a ngyɛb, ukwen, làbɔ̈ɔ̈n, anà nkääŋ a mpem.  
\v 13 Làkäl anà nkääŋ a mpem bɛ a bɛ, kya isàkal naa umwɛy uboo a bɛ we anà ikɔk a ndaa anà wumwɛy, làdwääl nkul bɛ a bɛ, asànaa kàladwääl Klistɔ, làkyer abun sye bɛ a bɛ.  
\v 14 Unsà ya yanswà, làkäl anà ukwen, wa wà asànaa un'siŋ a ngwal ufàlatüüb.  
\v 15 Wɛy duu a Klistɔ làyaal mpem abɛ, duu alà bàlabel bɛ banswà ntɔn mutɔŋ ndür mwɛy. Làyöb mufuur an'tɔɔn.  
\v 16 Wɛy ndaa a Klistɔ anà un'naaŋ aya wanswà ikäl amu bɛ! Làlɔŋàkà anà làweey amwɛy anà bumwɛy unsà an'yeerà manswà. Làtɔ̈ɔ̈l Nzam an'diim u mpem abɛ wanswà anà mfuur an'tɔɔn, u mbwo a an'diim, ikwɛŋ, anà an'diim ufàpà Dweelà.  
\v 17 Undiir wanswà lan'kwo bɛ mutɛn itàkal mukyer, làkyer wa kà ikɔb a Mwol Yɛsu, unsà mfuur an'tɔɔn akà Taa Nzam u mbwo a nde. 
\s1 Nkääl akün uboo a bɔr 
\p  
\v 18 Akaar, lawem adim abɛ, asànaa abà ukwen a Mwol. 
\p  
\v 19 Abaal, lakwen akyay abɛ, twon lan'kal anà itsumbuun akà ba. 
\p  
\v 20 Baan, làkäl anà unkyeey akà aböör abɛ unsà indiir byanswà, ntɔn ya ifàpà un'sak akà Mwol. 
\p  
\v 21 Bàtaa, twon lan'pà baan abɛ unkiiŋ, manà ba bàkɔ̈ɔ̈n ayàkal anà un'kanà. 
\p  
\v 22 Asɔ, làkäl anà unkyeey akà ankum abɛ unsà indiir byanswà u mɛɛn pà. Làkyer abun, kà nà u mpal bàlaseyà ba anki, asànaa bɛ làleŋà mupà un'sak akà baar, wɛɛ kà unsà mpem yweel anki, ntɔn bɛ làfàtiin Mwol bɔɔmà.  
\v 23 Itàkal naa isal abɛ akyɛy kyà kà aben, làkyer kya u mpem aŋàbwaŋ, ntɔn Mwol, wɛɛ kà ntɔn baar anki.  
\v 24 Làyöb naa bɛ làsàwal làfur akà Mwol, la là kwal kàlɔ̈ɔ̈n nde ntɔn aŋikyɛɛl. Ntɔn Nkum a ndandaa làsyääl bɛ wà Klistɔ.  
\v 25 Mbuur mpa awà balàbal asàwal làfur a nkɔ̈ɔ̈n a balàbal ande, un'kɔl aŋàyɔŋ watɛy. 
\c 4  
\p  
\v 1 Ankum, làkyer balàbal anà nkɔ̈ɔ̈n a nsöön akà asɔ abɛ, làyöb naa bɛ sye, bɛ làbye anà Nkum mwɛy u du. 
\s1 Nkääl akà baar abà u nsà 
\p  
\v 2 Làsi muküünà u ngyamàkà, amu ya, làkäl kà ikyɛɛŋ anà làfuur an'tɔɔn akà Nzam.  
\v 3 Mpal làyamà bɛ, làyamà sye ntɔn bi ntɔn Nzam kipɛ ipöl aŋàbwaŋ mulɔŋ ndaa ande, mukyään ngyee a Klistɔ, yà ntɔn ya in'wà mɛ u bɔlokà,  
\v 4 ntɔn mɛ in'sam ya ubwaŋàbwaŋ asànaa an'kwo mɛ musam ya. 
\p  
\v 5 Abà, làkäl anà an'yeerà unsà nkääl abɛ akà baar mpa abà aklistɔ, anà làsyääl taaŋ.  
\v 6 Wɛy an'yääm abɛ màkäl màŋàbwaŋ taaŋ lanswà, màŋàsà muŋ, anà nkwaar mufuur akà mbuur wanswà. 
\s1 Mbɔr a ntsüü 
\p  
\v 7 Tishik, un'tɔŋ wànkween, un'syääl mwɛy wàlää, un'baay amɛ unsà isal a Mwol, akyer ayàlasam làsaŋ amɛ lanswà.  
\v 8 Mɛ, mɛ amàlatööm awà abun ntɔn mukàlasam làsaŋ abi anà mukàlalɛɛl.  
\v 9 Ɔnɛsim, un'tɔŋ wàlää anà nkween, umwɛy uboo a bɛ, wàmuyà mbwo mwɛy anà nde. Ba bàyàlasam indiir byanswà ikalyaaŋà kà. 
\p  
\v 10 Aristark, awà u bɔlokà anà mɛ, kàmàlatööm mbɔr mbɔɔn, anà Malakɔ sye, un'tɔŋ a Barnabas. Bɛ làkyàwal nswɛɛŋ ntɔn nde : isàkal naa nde kan'yà akà bɛ, lun'wɛl ubwaŋàbwaŋ.  
\v 11 Yɛsu awà bàfàbel Yüstüs, kàmàlatööm mbɔr. Ba mpɛl uboo a Ayudà abàmusal anà mɛ ntɔn Imwol a Nzam. Ba bàkäl ndɛɛl ntɔn mɛ. 
\p  
\v 12 Ɛpafras, nde sye wà umwɛy uboo abɛ, un'syääl a Klistɔ mpa afàyɔn munwaan ità u ngyamàkà ande, ntɔn bɛ làkäl bàŋàtsim, bàŋàbwaŋ, anà ntɔn muswaŋ ngyööl a an'kyän a ukwen a Nzam banswà.  
\v 13 Mɛ amun'tɛɛl imbäl ki naa nde afàsal ngwal mbɔɔn ntɔn bɛ, ntɔn baar a bul a Lawɔdisɛ anà bà bul a Yɛlapɔlis.  
\v 14 Lukà, un'ngaŋ, un'saam abi anà Dɛmas bàmàlatööm mbɔr. 
\p  
\v 15 Apɛ atɔŋ abà u bul a Lawɔdisɛ mbɔr, anà Nɛmfa, anà Ikööŋ ifàköŋ u ndwà ande.  
\v 16 Mpal làsàmay bɛ mutaŋ un'kaan amɛ, làkyer mbwo yanswà naa bàtäŋ wa sye u Ikööŋ a Lawɔdisɛ. Làtäŋ sye anà wa akwà asàfà Lawɔdisɛ.  
\v 17 Abun, lun'kyään Arship naa: « Tà mpi isal kàwɛl ngye unsà Mwol, ntɔn ngye akwey kya ubwaŋàbwaŋ. » 
\p  
\v 18 Le mbɔr a kɔɔ amɛ Pɔl yayi: Làyɔbà naa mɛ in'wà u bɔlokà. Wɛy kab a ngway a Nzam làkäl anà bɛ!